{"word":"Asaph","slug":"asaph","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Asaph</b> <a href=\"#/H623\">H623</a> <br/> 1. Father of Joah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=18&verse=18'>2Ki 18:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=36&verse=3'>Isa 36:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=36&verse=22'>Isa 36:22</a><br/> 2. Son of Berachiah<br/> - One of the three leaders of music in David's organization of the tabernacle service<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=15&verse=19'>1Ch 15:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=16&verse=7'>1Ch 16:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=25&verse=9'>1Ch 25:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=5&verse=12'>2Ch 5:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=35&verse=15'>2Ch 35:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=46'>Neh 12:46</a> <br/> - Appointed to sound the cymbals in the temple choir<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=15&verse=17'>1Ch 15:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=15&verse=19'>1Ch 15:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=16&verse=5'>1Ch 16:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=16&verse=7'>1Ch 16:7</a> <br/> - A composer of sacred lyrics<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=29&verse=30'>2Ch 29:30</a> <br/> - Reference titles of Psalm 50 and Psalm 73-83<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=50'>Psa 50</a> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=73'>Psa 73</a> <br/> - Descendants of, in the temple choir<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=25&verse=9'>1Ch 25:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=20&verse=14'>2Ch 20:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=29&verse=13'>2Ch 29:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=2&verse=41'>Ezr 2:41</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=3&verse=10'>Ezr 3:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=7&verse=44'>Neh 7:44</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=11&verse=22'>Neh 11:22</a> <br/> 3. A Levite, whose descendants dwelt in Jerusalem after the exile<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=9&verse=15'>1Ch 9:15</a><br/> 4. A Kohath Levite<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=26&verse=1'>1Ch 26:1</a><br/> 5. Keeper of forests<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=2&verse=8'>Neh 2:8</a>"}]}